Shouts of Jagaban, City Boy rend the air as the Motorcade of the All Progressives Congress (APC) Presidential Candidate, Asiwaju Bola Ahmed Tinubu, and his running mate, Senator Kashim Shettima, arrived Teslim Balogun Stadium in Surulere, Lagos for the grand finale of TInubu’s campaign. The stadium was filled to the brim as crowd of supporters welcome Tinubu and other APC chieftains. Naira policy won’t have impact on Tinubu’s chances – Orji Kalu Aisha Buhari under fire for sharing fake CBN release on old notes The Motorcade departed the airport with crowd of supporters waving at him and cheering him up. The Motorcade drove from the airport through the Lagos-Abeokuta Expressway along Oshodi. He was in front of the vehicle with Shettima, Senate President, Ahmad Lawan and Speaker of the House of Representatives, Femi Gbajabiamila. They all waved to supporters from the double-decker APC branded bus. See some pictures below:    